Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:05.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:08.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:10.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case is about John the dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's a shepherd dog known\Nthroughout the neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:15.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dogs may not speak,\Nbut there's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder how old he is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was still just a puppy when I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'd say around 8 or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:09.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:13.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}John. I'm not high school student Shin'ichi Kudo anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:17.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm grade school student Conan Edogawa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since we ate out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That restaurant was pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is the place!\NThe house where John the dog lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were in grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi used to stop by here\Non his way home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would save some bread from lunch\Nand then give it to the dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masayoshi Sakaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard that name somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says he's a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a famous lawyer who specializes in cases involving minors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this the house where that middle school student killed himself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I was in third grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He jumped at Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in the way! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That tickles, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.74,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello? What's going on, Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:06.54,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.01,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? Conan{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in Izu on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just heard Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} screamâ€”what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come home right away!\NJohn's done something terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was Takeshi Maehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\N22 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a college student who lives\Nin the apartment complex next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked him\Nto watch the place while he was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} invited you,\NSanae Sugita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, could you give us the details\Nabout what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was around 8:00 when I came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've never been in such a huge living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aren't you glad you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Super glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was just getting fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sakaguchi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.08,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? John?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:28.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's at the top of the stairs, behaving himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? You want to talk to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:35.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}John! Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alright, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here, your master wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then we showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would the dog suddenly attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only think that he attacked Takeshi for no reason at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! John would never attack anyone for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Takeshi didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to the dog, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say anything for sure yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if he really attacked for no reason as she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then he'll probably have to be put to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put to sleep? You're going to kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we first need to talk to Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"First year middle school student kills himself."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Was bullying the cause?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"...a classmate that bullied Masato{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}â€”"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:03.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It doesn't give the bully's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}John's been well trained,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and he'd never attack anyone for no reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:15.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}John attacked the victim immediately\Nafter the phone was put to his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:20.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} ordered\NJohn to attack over the phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:24.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} always seems so nice;\Nhe'd never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's John, Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't put him to sleep already, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been taken to the police station for now;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it hasn't been decided that he's to be put to sleep yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Inspector. What did Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says he can't believe that John would attack anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither can I! There must be a reason whyâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please continue, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:08:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked Mr. Sakaguchi about his phone conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To start off, what exactly did you say to the victim over the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:09.25,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I asked him if everything was alright,\Nhow John was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and then I asked him to put John on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:18.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I always say good night to him,\Nso I thought I'd say it tonight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So you told John good night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:25.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before that, I think I asked,\N"How are you doing, John?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:31.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then suddenly I heard John bark\Nand Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10} scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl who was there confirmed his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mentioned it last night,\Ndidn't you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s son committed suicide a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked him about that at the station too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said a bully drove him to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:09:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe his son's bully was Takeshi Maehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's still just a "maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard this directly from Mr. Sakaguchi himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His son Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Takeshi Maehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were classmates in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} apparently wrote about Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} in his diary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,shortly before hanging himself in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that Mr. Sakaguchi loathed Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} after reading the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since his wife had died early on,\NMasato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was all he had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when he saw Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} crying and apologizing at the funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he decided to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was the only one\Nwho bullied Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shortly after, Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} moved to Kansai
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because of his father's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, two years ago, he moved back to attend a university in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was this spring that he moved into an apartment complex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right next to the Sakaguchi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:10:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It truly was an act of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently Mr. Sakaguchi was surprised by the unexpected reunion, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he no longer bore any\Nill feelings toward Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm even told that he sometimes invited him over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he really does still have\Na grudge against Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sakaguchi secretly trained John to attack people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when a specific phrase is said to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then last night, he said that phrase to John over the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:34.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How are you doing, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this way, Mr. Sakaguchi accomplished his revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I questioned him last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he repeated what he said on the phone,\Nright in front of John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John didn't react one bit when he heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gah! I thought I sounded so authoritative too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't feel so down in the dumps, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you might be lonely without John to keep you company!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, does John always sleep at the top of the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't he sleep downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See that door there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was my son's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He absolutely loved John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his late mother said\Nhe couldn't let the dog in his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:12:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so John always slept in front of his door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John's still waiting for him to open the door\Nand say good morning to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it's been eight years\Nsince my son died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's a big phone over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The receiver's connected to it by a cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, wasn't there a cordless phone there last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I sometimes switch it with the phone in my study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This guy really didâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:46.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The clock must've struck 9:00 just before it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I see how Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} ordered John to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone was different?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The receiver on the big phone\Nis connected by a cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But last night he had a cordless phone there, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? There's probably no real reasonâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} absolutely needed it to be a cordless phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen. It would be impossible to carry a regular phone up a staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} purposely placed a portable cordless phone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you still think that Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nused John to commit a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely certain of it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't know the most important thingâ€”\Nhow he ordered the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, our clock doesn't chime, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clock in Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s living room\Nchimes real loud every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His {\i1}clock{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was precisely 9:00 when John attacked Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The great detective, Kogoro Mouri, has just solved the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Beika Police Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I give the word,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,repeat what you said to John last night on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you doing, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you doing, John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Were my deductions all wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so certain of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You overanalyzed things, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would never use the dog\Nthat his son loved to get revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say anything for certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but what we found out from our investigation afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was that Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} supposedly took John somewhere in his car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,every Sunday for the last three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to him, he took John\Nto the outskirts of town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and let him get a lot of exercise in the empty fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! He obviously trained John during those times!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry to have to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's been decided that John is to be put to sleep tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sakaguchi understands as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}John, the dog you liked so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:20.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is going to be killed if we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please come back, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:28.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're the only one who can save John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they're going to kill John this evening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't we do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was up all night thinking about it too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've finally figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think he figured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have another test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}On your mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Get set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now say the words, if you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you admit you trained John\Nto attack Takeshi Maehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't remember me, or Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had completely forgotten about\Nthe very person he drove to suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he unwittingly moved into\Nthe apartment complex next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a lawyer who specializes\Nin crimes committed by minors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took this job so that I could help\Nyoung people who lost their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when I saw him crying and apologizing at the funeral 8 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was still just a 1st-year middle school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I felt that Masato's death wouldn't be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if he truly regretted it with all his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I met him again 8 years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he didn't remember a single thing about the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only that, he was no different than he was eight years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Give me my wallet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm just borrowing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:23.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stop worrying! I'll pay you back one of these days, when I feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:26.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who knows when that'll be, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw that, I could feel my blood boil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was Masato's death for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I ever forgive him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then you used Johnâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided that if the law couldn't deal with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then I would take justice into my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure that John was happy that he avenged Masato too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't the only one who was sad when Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} died!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how sad John was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said so yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, John still waits for Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} in front of his door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you honestly think that Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you used his loyal dog to kill someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Bullying is definitely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I actually do understand your ill will toward Takeshi Maehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But did you ever once think about the feelings of the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you stupidly used as a murder tool to get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John is saying that he still cares for you, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please try to understand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they didn't kill John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was taken in by one of Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s relatives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's all thanks to Kogoro Mouri, the great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:22:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But John doesn't live at that house anymore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:23:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad. We really liked him a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can always make friends with another dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Look at that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks just like John!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You appear to have quite an exceptional dog, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm a dog-lover myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you say we talk about dogs at that coffee shop over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sic 'im, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Go start a relationship with a dog instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two took a bath together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sure was fun, scrubbing each other's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nosebleed? The bath must've rushed the blood to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm dead if she finds out who I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No question about it!
